<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Na lung nih lawmhnak darkhing thawng a theih lai, Dinhnak na sin in a
 then bal ti lai lo, Kutka bi lei tu panh law, Jesuh ca nifa nung tuah, Na
 lung ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng a thang lai

[C1]
   Lawmhnak darkhing na theih lai, (darkhing na theih lai), Lawmhnak
   darkhing na theih lai. Khuazei ka na kal hmanh ah, Khamhtu min kha i lak
   law, Na lung ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng na theih lai.

[V2]
 A tlingmi Jesuh dawtnak cu na hngalh lai, Hi dawtnak cu na velchum ah
 a lang lai, Dawtnak bianem chim zungzal, Vel he nifa riantuan tuah, Na
 lung ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng a thang lai.

[C2]
   Lawmhnak darkhing na theih lai, (darkhing na theih lai), Lawmhnak
   darkhing na theih lai. Khuazei ka na kal hmanh ah, Khamhtu min kha i lak
   law, Na lung ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng na theih lai.

[V3]
 Na kalnk van lam ah harnak um hmanhseh, A vel cu tam chin in chin in
 na sin an pek lai, Mit hmuh lo a si nain, Na sin a um an naih ko, Na lung
 ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng a thang lai.

[C3]
   Lawmhnak darkhing na theih lai, (darkhing na theih lai), Lawmhnak
   darkhing na theih lai. Khuazei ka na kal hmanh ah, Khamhtu min kha i lak
   law, Na lung ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng na theih lai.

[V4]
 Na nunnak cu Jesuh kong chim in hmang tuah, A dinnak cu ngei law mi va
 phaw ve hna, Nunnak thiang na ngeih ahcun, misual na bawmh khawh hna lai
 Na lung-lawmhnak darkhing thawng a thang lai.

[C4]
   Lawmhnak darkhing na theih lai, (darkhing na theih lai), Lawmhnak
   darkhing na theih lai. Khuazei ka na kal hmanh ah, Khamhtu min kha i lak
   law, Na lung ah lawmhnak darkhing thawng na theih lai.</lyrics>
